overview: Messer in the mountains  Separated by destiny, apart, the companions try in their day jobs to make different paths to get to the same place. And after the journey, from the reunion, comes the return of the music, which packs the preparations for what would be the end for them.  Third video of the series "Messer In Concert", recorded between the years 2017 and 2019.
title: Messer In The Mountains
